About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. “Alpha”, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. “Alpha”, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

Pardesiya..
Hai tere pyar mein jab se
Jhankaar si..
Hai dil ke taar mein tab se

Tum ho mere jaanta hun magar

Kab se hun main ummeed meiñ
Hai ankaha jo sun lo agar

Mila hai tu mujhe jab se

Maiñ qaid huñ

Qaabu mein kar liya

Maiñ qaid huñ
Tere bhi pyar mein tab se ..

Pardesiya haiñ teri batiyoñ ne 
Kiya pareshan pardesiya..

Pardesiya haiñ teri ankhiyoñ ke
Dil pe nishaan pardesiya..
 
Chhoo ke laboñ se jaise
Jaadu hi kar diya
Saavan ne morni ko
Qaabu mein kar liya

Hum dono ki juda theeñ hastiyaañ
Hoñ kinara bin jaise kashtiyaañ

Aasaan ho aage safar
Tum saath mera chun lo agar

Pardesiya.. 

#SonuNigam #SidharthMalhotra #JanhviKapoor

snippet.title: The Conjuring: Last Rites | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover why this case ended it all. #TheConjuring: Last Rites - Only in Theaters September 5.

From New Line Cinema comes the ninth entry in the more than $2 billion theatrical Conjuring universe, The Conjuring: Last Rites, directed by franchise veteran Michael Chaves and produced by franchise architects James Wan and Peter Safran.

The Conjuring: Last Rites delivers another thrilling chapter of the iconic Conjuring cinematic universe, based on real events.  Vera Farmiga and Patrick Wilson reunite for one last case as renowned, real-life paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren in a powerful and spine-chilling addition to the global box office-breaking franchise.

Farmiga and Wilson star alongside Mia Tomlinson and Ben Hardy, who portray Ed and Lorraine’s daughter Judy Warren and her boyfriend, Tony Spera, as well as Steve Coulter returning as Father Gordon, Rebecca Calder, Elliot Cowan, Kíla Lord Cassidy, Beau Gadsdon, John Brotherton and Shannon Kook.

Chaves directs from a screenplay by Ian Goldberg & Richard Naing and David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, story by David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick & James Wan, based on characters created by Chad Hayes & Carey W. Hayes.  The executive producers are Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Hans Ritter, David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, Natalia Safran, John Rickard and Michael Chaves.

Chaves is joined behind the camera by his creative team, including director of photography Eli Born, production designer John Frankish, editors Elliot Greenberg and Gregory Plotkin, visual effects supervisor Scott Edelstein, visual effects producer Eric Bruneau and costume designer Graham Churchyard, with casting by Rose Wicksteed and Sophie Kingston-Smith.  The music supervisor is Ian Broucek and the music is by composer Benjamin Wallfisch.

New Line Cinema Presents The Safran Company / An Atomic Monster Production, The Conjuring: Last Rites.  The film will be released worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and will be only in theaters and IMAX® in North America on September 5, 2025, and internationally beginning 3 September 2025.

snippet.title: लालू जी की LOVE Story | Official Trailer | Yash Kumarr, Nidhi Jha | New Bhojpuri Movie 2025
snippet.description:
🎬 Official Trailer – "लालू जी की LOVE Story" | A Bhojpuri Romantic Drama | Yash Kumarr & Nidhi Jha

तन्वी मल्टीमीडिया प्रस्तुत करती है 2025 की सबसे दिलचस्प प्रेम कहानी – "लालू जी की LOVE Story", जिसमें रोमांस है, कॉमेडी है और परिवार का प्यारा तड़का।

🎥 फिल्म क्रेडिट्स:
तन्वी मल्टीमीडिया 
◾निर्माता - दीपक शाह 
◾निर्देशक - सुजीत वर्मा 
◾संगीत - साजन मिश्रा व मुन्ना दुबे 
◾गीत - आशुतोष तिवारी,राजेश मिश्रा 
◾गायक - विजय चौहान,प्रियंका सिंह,सिंगधा सरकार,खुशबू जैन 
◾संवाद व पाठकथा - राकेश त्रिपाठी 
◾कथा - यश कुमार 
◾छायंकन - समीर जहांगीर सैयद
◾संकलन - गुरजेंट सिंह
◾नूत्य - प्रवीण शेलार
◾कार्यकारी निर्माता - शैलेंद्र सिंह
◾कला - अवधेश राय
◾ड्रेस डिज़ायनर - नानू फ़ैशन(विद्या-विष्णु)
◾प्रचारक - रंजन शिन्हा 
◾पब्लिसिट डिज़ाइनर - सूरज गिरी
◾रूप सज्जा - ख़लील रहमान
◾रेकोडिस्ट - अशोक यादव
◾डी आई - इन्द्रजीत यादव
◾पोस्ट प्रडक्शन - आई फ़ोकस स्टूडीओ(विजय दिनेश) व वोट प्रोडक्शन

👉 ये ट्रेलर देखें और जानें क्या है लालू जी की लव स्टोरी में ख़ास।
🎧 बेहतरीन संगीत, ज़बरदस्त डायलॉग्स और मस्त कहानी।

📢 अब ट्रेंडिंग में लाने के लिए वीडियो को लाइक करें, शेयर करें और कमेंट ज़रूर करें!

💑 कहानी:
“लालू जी की LOVE Story” एक साधारण लेकिन बेहद दिलचस्प युवक लालू की कहानी है, जो अपने सीधेपन, मासूमियत और बेइंतहा प्यार के चलते एक अनोखी प्रेम यात्रा पर निकल पड़ता है। यह सिर्फ लव स्टोरी नहीं, बल्कि एक भावनात्मक rollercoaster है जिसमें कॉमेडी, ड्रामा और रिश्तों की गहराई है।

🌟 मुख्य भूमिकाओं में:
◾ Yash Kumarr – एक बार फिर अपने अनोखे अंदाज़ में
◾ Nidhi Jha – शानदार अदायगी के साथ
उनकी ऑनस्क्रीन केमिस्ट्री इस फिल्म का प्रमुख आकर्षण है।

तन्वी मल्टीमीडिया प्रस्तुत करती है 2025 की सबसे दिलचस्प प्रेम कहानी – "लालू जी की LOVE Story", जिसमें रोमांस है, कॉमेडी है और परिवार का प्यारा तड़का।

🎥 फिल्म क्रेडिट्स:
तन्वी मल्टीमीडिया 
◾निर्माता - दीपक शाह 
◾निर्देशक - सुजीत वर्मा 
◾संगीत - साजन मिश्रा व मुन्ना दुबे 
◾गीत - आशुतोष तिवारी,राजेश मिश्रा 
◾गायक - विजय चौहान,प्रियंका सिंह,सिंगधा सरकार,खुशबू जैन 
◾संवाद व पाठकथा - राकेश त्रिपाठी 
◾कथा - यश कुमार 
◾छायंकन - समीर जहांगीर सैयद
◾संकलन - गुरजेंट सिंह
◾नूत्य - प्रवीण शेलार
◾कार्यकारी निर्माता - शैलेंद्र सिंह
◾कला - अवधेश राय
◾ड्रेस डिज़ायनर - नानू फ़ैशन(विद्या-विष्णु)
◾प्रचारक - रंजन शिन्हा 
◾पब्लिसिट डिज़ाइनर - सूरज गिरी
◾रूप सज्जा - ख़लील रहमान
◾रेकोडिस्ट - अशोक यादव
◾डी आई - इन्द्रजीत यादव
◾पोस्ट प्रडक्शन - आई फ़ोकस स्टूडीओ(विजय दिनेश) व वोट प्रोडक्शन

👉 ये ट्रेलर देखें और जानें क्या है लालू जी की लव स्टोरी में ख़ास।
🎧 बेहतरीन संगीत, ज़बरदस्त डायलॉग्स और मस्त कहानी।

📢 अब ट्रेंडिंग में लाने के लिए वीडियो को लाइक करें, शेयर करें और कमेंट ज़रूर करें!

💑 कहानी:
“लालू जी की LOVE Story” एक साधारण लेकिन बेहद दिलचस्प युवक लालू की कहानी है, जो अपने सीधेपन, मासूमियत और बेइंतहा प्यार के चलते एक अनोखी प्रेम यात्रा पर निकल पड़ता है। यह सिर्फ लव स्टोरी नहीं, बल्कि एक भावनात्मक rollercoaster है जिसमें कॉमेडी, ड्रामा और रिश्तों की गहराई है।

🌟 मुख्य भूमिकाओं में:
◾ Yash Kumarr – एक बार फिर अपने अनोखे अंदाज़ में
◾ Nidhi Jha – शानदार अदायगी के साथ
उनकी ऑनस्क्रीन केमिस्ट्री इस फिल्म का प्रमुख आकर्षण है।

🏆 GRAND FINALS DAY 2 | AUGUST 2

The 2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP reaches its ultimate stage — the Grand Finals Day 2 begins today in Riyadh! After days of fierce competition, the top 16 teams in the world have earned their place to fight for glory, legacy, and the lion’s share of the $3,000,000 prize pool.

After days of fierce competition, the top 16 PUBG MOBILE teams on the globe have secured their place in this final stage — chasing glory, legacy, and a share of the $3,000,000 prize pool. This is the moment every team has been grinding for and one day is already behind. The best from the Group Stage and the survivors of the Survival Stage should keep go head-to-head in the most intense showdown of the year. Three days, SMASH RULE, and one champion.

The journey rechs a new height — because only one team will lift the trophy and etch their name into PUBG MOBILE history. Let the Grand Finals Day 2 begin.

 🔥 How does SMASH RULE work? 
After today’s matches are over (Day 2 of Grand Finals), the Match Point Threshold will be set to the #1 ranked team’s points +10. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy—winning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn’t bring the championship. If no team secures the title via SMASH Rule by Match 18, the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

🔥 Why You Can’t Miss 2025 PMWC at EWC:
- The top 16 teams on one stage — no second chances!
- Every match counts in the race for the championship!
- Witness PUBG MOBILE history in the making!
- Explosive SMASH RULE format — pressure-packed, winner-takes-all action!

snippet.title: Hobe Na Dekha | হবে না দেখা | Dhumketu | Dev | Subhashree | Ishan Mitra | Anupam Roy | Bengali Song
snippet.description:
শুনুন দেব-শুভশ্রী অভিনীত নতুন ছবি, ধুমকেতু থেকে হৃদয় ছুঁয়ে যাওয়া একটি নতুন বাংলা গান "হবে না দেখা", যেখানে কণ্ঠ দিয়েছেন ইশান মিত্র এবং সুর ও কথা সাজিয়েছেন প্রখ্যাত সুরকার-গীতিকার অনুপম রায়। 

Presenting the heartfelt new Bengali song "Hobe Na Dekha", a beautifully emotional track that captures the pain of longing and the silence of separation. With evocative lyrics and a stirring composition by Anupam Roy, this song finds its perfect voice in the soulful singing of Ishan Mitra.

আপনার পছন্দের ভালো গান শুনতে সাবস্ক্রাইব করুন  @saregamabengali

Song Name :- Hobe Na Dekha
Singer : Ishan Mitra
Music & Lyrics : Anupam Roy
Arrangement & programming : Shamik Chakravarty
Acoustic guitar & dotara : John Paul
Mixed & mastered by Anindit Roy

Flim Credits:-

snippet.title: New Adivasi Song | Asli Aadiwasi ( असली आदिवासी ) | Aadiwood | Aadiwasi Diwasi Song  #adivasisong
snippet.description:
🙏 धन-धन सतगुरु | जय जोहार, जय आदिवासी 🌿

Aadiwood Production (The Brand of Nimar) proudly presents:

Our New Song Asli Aadiwasi a soul-stirring Adivasi song in the powerful voices of Bheem Kanoje and Pradnya Jadhav. This Barela-language song, written by Bheem Kanoje, celebrates Adivasi culture, traditions, attire, music, and lifestyle with deep authenticity.

The music is beautifully composed by Ritesh Chouhan, and the video is directed by Rohit Vaishaki. The song is a true tribute to the indigenous identity of India.

🙏 सेवा ज़ोहार साथियों 🏹
9 अगस्त - विश्व आदिवासी दिवस हमारे लिए अत्यंत महत्वपूर्ण दिन है, जिसे UNO ने घोषित किया है। इस दिन का उद्देश्य हमारी संस्कृति, परंपराओं और आदिवासी समाज की पहचान को सम्मान देना है। हमें अपनी जड़ों, रीति-रिवाजों और आदिवासी जीवनशैली का आदर करना चाहिए, ताकि हम अपने इतिहास और संस्कृति को सहेज कर रख सकें।
यह वीडियो गाना किसी एक व्यक्ति द्वारा नहीं, बल्कि आदिवासी विचारधारा को मानने वाली एक युवा टीम द्वारा तैयार किया गया है। "Asli Aadiwasi" गीत हमें हमारी संस्कृति और परंपराओं से जुड़ा होने का गर्व महसूस कराता है।

Song Credits :-
Title: Asli Aadiwasi
Singers: Bheem Kanoje, Pradnya Jadhav
Lyrics: Bheem Kanoje
Music Composer & Audio Mixing: Ritesh Chouhan
Video Director: Rohit Vaishaki

Instrumentation Team -:
Flute: Anupam Wankhede
Guitar/Ukulele: Prarabdh Tiwari
Beat Producer: DJ Arun More (Arun More)

Creative Team :-
Choreography: Karan Solanki, Mayur Singh Chouhan
Director of Photography (DOP): KM Photography (Karan More)
Makeup Artist: Rupaly Senani
Costume Designers: Sukhlal Solanki, Nirmla Solanki, Golu Rathor
Digital Partner: Adivasi Media – Agesh Solanki

Filming Locations :-
Chatli, Panjrya, Ajgiriya (Dhavli), Niwali, Khadi Kham, Sendhwa

Cast & Crew Team :-
Featured Artists: Priya Solanki, Mayur Singh Chouhan, Sakshi Bhandari, Aashu Bamne
Child Artists: Navya Vaishaki, Aarushi Bamne, Rajnandini Bamne, Aarush Bamne, Chotu Bamne
Special Appearances: Soniya Arjoon Solanki, Rahul Kavche, Ram Senani

Dance Group Members & Support Crew:
(Full team is credited to honor every contributor.)

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/aadiwood.offical.7

snippet.title: Coolie Trailer Tamil Live - Coolie Audio Launch | RajiniKanth | Lokesh Kanagaraj | Sun Pictures |
snippet.description:
Coolie, headlined by Superstar Rajinikanth and directed by Lokesh Kanagaraj, is easily the most awaited Tamil film of the year. The movie is carrying massive hype in Telugu as well. The USA pre-sales are remarkable, and now Canada has joined the party. The Telugu version alone has grossed over $100K so far.

Anirudh, Lokesh, and the team have already started promoting the biggie through media interviews. The latest and shocking update is that the film has been rated ‘A’ (Adults Only) by the Central Board of Film Certification (CBFC). No one saw this coming, and the news is now making waves on social media.

Is the ‘A’ certificate due to extreme violence or some other reason? We’ll have to wait for the censor certificate for more details. This also marks the first-ever film by Lokesh Kanagaraj to receive an A certificate. With expectations already sky-high, this latest development will only amplify the buzz. The film, also starring Aamir Khan, Nagarjuna, Upendra, and Shruti Haasan, is set to release on August 14.


On Saturday, the makers of the film 'Coolie', Sun Pictures, posted a carousel post where they announced the trailer release timings. According to the given details, the Coolie movie trailer will be released at 7 PM IST, ahead of the film's grand audio launch event in Chennai. The caption of the post reads, "Coolie varraan solliko! The day is here! #CoolieTrailer from today 7 PM."

snippet.title: शनि देव कथा | शनि महाराज की अद्भुत कथा | Shani Dev Katha in Hindi
snippet.description:
🌑 शनि देव कथा | शनि महाराज की अद्भुत कथा | Shani Dev Katha in Hindi 🌑

🙏 शनि महाराज, कर्मों के फल देने वाले न्यायाधीश, जिनकी पूजा और भक्ति से जीवन में आती है शांति, समृद्धि और सुरक्षा।
इस अद्भुत कथा में जानिए शनि देव की महिमा, उनके न्यायप्रिय स्वभाव और उनके प्रकोप व कृपा के रहस्यों को।

✨ इस वीडियो में आप सुनेंगे:
🔹 शनि देव की उत्पत्ति और उनकी न्यायप्रियता की कथा
🔹 शनि दोष से मुक्ति पाने के उपाय और शनि व्रत का महत्व
🔹 शनि देव की कृपा से जुड़ी चमत्कारिक घटनाएं
🔹 शनिवार के दिन शनि देव की पूजा और व्रत की विधि

🪔 शनिवार को यह कथा सुनना अत्यंत शुभ माना जाता है। इसे सुनकर शनि महाराज की कृपा प्राप्त करें और अपने जीवन को सफल बनाएं।

🔔 चैनल को सब्सक्राइब करें और बेल आइकन दबाएं ताकि आपको ऐसे आध्यात्मिक और प्रेरणादायक वीडियो सबसे पहले मिलें।

🙏 कृपया इस वीडियो को लाइक, शेयर और कमेंट करें ताकि अधिक से अधिक लोग शनि देव की कृपा से लाभान्वित हो सकें।

#ShaniDevKatha #ShaniMaharaj #ShaniBhakti #ShaniVrat #BhaktiKatha #ShaniDevStory

Coolie is an 2025 Indian Tamil-language action thriller film directed by Lokesh Kanagaraj and produced by Kalanithi Maran under Sun Pictures. The film stars Rajinikanth, Nagarjuna, Upendra, Soubin Shahir, Sathyaraj and Shruti Haasan in lead roles, alongside Reba Monica John, Junior MGR, Kanna Ravi, Monisha Blessy and Kaali Venkat.

Coolie is scheduled to release worldwide on 14 August 2025.

snippet.title: UNLUCKY 13?! 😱 Clash-A-Rama 13th Clashiversary Special Episode!
snippet.description:
Giant sinkholes are tearing up this party! But that won't stop us celebrating the 13th Clashiversary... Clash-A-Rama style! You've watched it. Now play it!


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

snippet.title: Spider-Man: Alone | Official Teaser Trailer (Fan-Series)
snippet.description:
Be the first to know when we launch! Follow our Indiegogo Pre-Launch Page: [https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/spider-man-alone-episode-1/coming_soon/]

Happy National Spider-Man Day! From Golden Century Films and our "Marvel Inspire" universe, this is the official teaser trailer for 'Spider-Man: Alone.'

Season 1 of 'Spider-Man: Alone' is a deeply personal, character-driven fan series that plunges into the heart of Peter Parker's earliest days. A modern, street-level reimagining of Amazing Fantasy #15, our story explores the profound isolation and immense weight of newfound powers. This is the story of a boy learning to fly, and the agonizing, often lonely, process of what it cost him to become a hero.

This project is also proud to launch our Inspired Action initiative in partnership with the non-profit Friendly Neighborhood Activist, aiming to turn on-screen heroism into real-world change.

Follow the Journey & Join Our Community:
► Instagram: [https://www.instagram.com/goldencenturyfilms/]
► Twitter/X: [https://x.com/GoldenCenturyTV?t=nvrx03KCKC60Z4TcAYX5KA&s=09]
► Facebook: [https://www.facebook.com/share/1GUwgCDW4o/]

About This Project:

'Spider-Man: Alone' is a non-profit fan series. This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to Marvel, Sony, or any of their subsidiaries. It is a passion project created by fans, for fans, in celebration of a character who has inspired us our entire lives. The pilot will be available for free.

#SpiderManAlone #FanFilm #SpiderMan #Marvel #Sony #TeaserTrailer #IndieFilm #ComingSoon #StreetLevelSpiderMan #BrandNewDay #SupportIndieFilm #Crowdfunding #NationalSpiderManDay

Happy National Spider-Man Day! From Golden Century Films and our "Marvel Inspire" universe, this is the official teaser trailer for 'Spider-Man: Alone.'

Season 1 of 'Spider-Man: Alone' is a deeply personal, character-driven fan series that plunges into the heart of Peter Parker's earliest days. A modern, street-level reimagining of Amazing Fantasy #15, our story explores the profound isolation and immense weight of newfound powers. This is the story of a boy learning to fly, and the agonizing, often lonely, process of what it cost him to become a hero.

This project is also proud to launch our Inspired Action initiative in partnership with the non-profit Friendly Neighborhood Activist, aiming to turn on-screen heroism into real-world change.

Follow the Journey & Join Our Community:
► Instagram: [https://www.instagram.com/goldencenturyfilms/]
► Twitter/X: [https://x.com/GoldenCenturyTV?t=nvrx03KCKC60Z4TcAYX5KA&s=09]
► Facebook: [https://www.facebook.com/share/1GUwgCDW4o/]

About This Project:

'Spider-Man: Alone' is a non-profit fan series. This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to Marvel, Sony, or any of their subsidiaries. It is a passion project created by fans, for fans, in celebration of a character who has inspired us our entire lives. The pilot will be available for free.

snippet.title: Jignesh Barot | Mane Mara Prem Per Vishwash Che | જીગ્નેશ બારોટ | New Gujarati Love Song 2025
snippet.description:
જીગ્નેશ બારોટનું નવું ગીત "મને મારા પ્રેમ પર વિશ્વાસ છે" સાંભળો અને પ્રેમની મીઠી લાગણીઓ અનુભવો માત્ર @SaregamaGujarati  પર. 💖🎶

Credits:
Singer: Jignesh Barot
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Artists: Jignesh Barot, Riya Jaiswal, Piyush Patel
Co-Artists: Jitu Variya, Janavi Patel
Concept Director: Shankar Thakor Borisanawala
Lyrics: Rajan Rayaka, Dhaval Motan
Music: Jitu Prajapati
Creative Producer: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya
DOP: Atul Thakor
Drone: Pintu Zala
Editor: Kishor Rajput
Making: Pintu
BTS Editing: Jayanti Khoraj
AD & Art: Babusinh Thakor
Makeup & Hair: Lata Patel
Spot Boys: Arvind Gohel, Dilip Rathod, Mukesh Makwana
Poster: Aman Agora
Jignesh Barot Costume: Ekta J. Barot
Travels: Rudra Mahakal
Light: Kalpesh Jadav & Irfan (Baroda)
Thanks: Faresinh Rathva
Special Thanks: J. D. Bapu

Lyrics:
ઓ કટકા થાય કે જટકા તોયે દોડી આવશે (૩)
મને મારા પ્રેમ રે ઉપર વિશ્વાસ છે 
ઓ મરશે પણ ફરસે નહીં કોઈ ના રોકાશે(૨)
મને મારા પ્રેમ રે ઉપર વિશ્વાસ છે 
ઓ હું એને બોલાવું આયા વગર ના રહેશે 
જીવ ના જોખમ મેં પ્રેમ રે નિભાવશે 
મને મારા પ્રેમ રે ઉપર વિશ્વાસ છે 
ઓ કટકા થાય કે જટકા તોયે દોડી આવશે (૨)
મને મારા પ્રેમ રે ઉપર વિશ્વાસ છે 
ઓ રૂમ માં ભલે પુરીદો તાળું ભલે મારીદો 
ઘર ની પાછલી બારી એ થી ઉતરી ને આવશે 
ઓ દિવસ ને જવાદો રાત આખી જવા દો 
પરોઢિયા ના ૫ વાગે મળવા ને આવશે 
એનો મારો પ્રેમ તો જગ જાહેર રેહશે 
જુદા પાડવા વાડા હવે ઠબકાર રહેશે 
મને મારા પ્રેમ રે ઉપર વિશ્વાસ છે 
ઓ કટકા થાય કે જટકા તોયે દોડી આવશે 
મને મારા પ્રેમ રે ઉપર વિશ્વાસ છે 
ઓ પ્રેમ બહુ કરે છે મારા ઉપર મરે છે 
સોગંધ એના આલી મને સિગરેટ છોડાવે છે 
ઓ મારી આંખે ભળતી વાયદો એ પાડતી 
ચપ્પલ પહેરિયા વગર ઉઘાડા પેગે આવતી 
ભલે આવે પ્રેમ મા તુફાન કે આંધી 
મળવા આવશે ઓઢણી થી મોઢું રે બાંધી 
મને મારા પ્રેમ રે ઉપર વિશ્વાસ છે 
ઓ કટકા થાય કે જટકા તોયે દોડી આવશે (૩)
મને મારા પ્રેમ રે ઉપર વિશ્વાસ છે 
ઓ મરશે પણ ફરસે નહીં કોઈ ના રોકાશે(૨)
